    <div class="container">
        <h1>Project Management Skills as a Business Analyst</h1>

        <div class="project">
            <h2>Project Title: Logistics Management System Optimization</h2>
            <h3>Role: Business Analyst</h3>
            <h4>Duration: 8 months</h4>
            <p><strong>Project Description:</strong> Optimized the existing Logistics Management System for a major logistics company, addressing inefficiencies in shipment tracking and delivery scheduling.</p>

            <h4>Key Responsibilities:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Conducted requirements gathering with logistics coordinators and IT teams.</li>
                <li>Performed gap analysis to identify areas for system improvement.</li>
                <li>Redesigned logistics workflows for better shipment tracking and fleet management.</li>
                <li>Communicated effectively with stakeholders at all levels.</li>
                <li>Led User Acceptance Testing (UAT) to ensure functionality met requirements.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Project Outcome:</h4>
            <p class="outcome">Increased delivery efficiency by 20% and reduced operational costs by 15%.</p>

            <h4>Skills Utilized:</h4>
            <p class="skills">Agile methodologies, stakeholder management, data analysis, process redesign, UAT leadership.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="project">
            <h2>Project Title: Warehouse Management System Improvement</h2>
            <h3>Role: Business Analyst</h3>
            <h4>Duration: 6 months</h4>
            <p><strong>Project Description:</strong> Enhanced the Warehouse Management System to improve inventory tracking and order fulfillment processes.</p>

            <h4>Key Responsibilities:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Engaged with warehouse staff to identify operational pain points.</li>
                <li>Conducted gap analysis to compare system capabilities against industry standards.</li>
                <li>Redesigned inventory management processes for better accuracy.</li>
                <li>Facilitated training sessions for staff on new system features.</li>
                <li>Supported UAT and final implementation of system changes.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Project Outcome:</h4>
            <p class="outcome">Improved order fulfillment speed by 25% and reduced inventory discrepancies by 15%.</p>

            <h4>Skills Utilized:</h4>
            <p class="skills">Project management, process improvement, communication, training facilitation, analytical skills.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
